Mike D'Antoni on Utah forcing James Harden right (like Milwaukee):<br />
<br />
&quot;We've seen (that strategy) a little bit more often now and James just adjusts to it... He just figures it out...  You're not stopping him. I don't care what you do.&quot;

James Harden on Utah overplaying his right hand and trying to take away his step-back:<br />
<br />
&quot;I'm not surprised at anything. I've seen literally every defense you can possible see. It's just a matter of adjusting.&quot;

